OL,3,CFather's plea for daughter to receive
OL,4,Csurgery to fit specialist feeding tube
OL,6,FViewers are advised they may find some
OL,7,Fof the images in this report
OL,8,Fdistressing.
OL,10,FThe father of a four-year-old girl is
OL,11,Fmaking an emotional appeal to the
OL,12,FBelfast Trust to accept his daughter
OL,13,Ffor surgery to fit a specialist
OL,14,Ffeeding tube.
OL,16,FJoniece Sheppard, who has cerebral
OL,17,Fpalsy, spends much of her life in
OL,18,Fhospital because her body is rejecting
OL,19,Fwhat she is fed through her current
OL,20,Ftube.
