OL,3,CFather's plea for daughter to receive
OL,4,Csurgery to fit specialist feeding tube
OL,6,FJoniece's family have been told the
OL,7,Fwait for the procedure is up to five
OL,8,Fyears.
OL,10,FHer dad told UTV his little girl can't
OL,11,Fwait that long.
OL,13,FMatthew Sheppard said: "She's just not
OL,14,Fthe bubbly wee child she was every
OL,15,Fday."
OL,17,FJoniece has been approved for an
OL,18,Falternative.
OL,20,FMatthew believes what's called a PEG
OL,21,Ftube will solve many of her problems.
