OL,3,CFather's plea for daughter to receive
OL,4,Csurgery to fit specialist feeding tube
OL,6,FIt requires surgery to be fitted but
OL,7,Fthe waiting list is five years - and
OL,8,FJoniece is not considered a priority.
OL,10,FIn a statement, the Belfast Trust
OL,11,Fsaid: "Belfast Trust is very sorry
OL,12,Fthat any patient has to wait for
OL,13,Fsurgery.
OL,15,F"The Royal Belfast Hospital for Sick
OL,16,FChildren works with a number of
OL,17,Fspecialist medical professionals in
OL,18,FBelfast Trust and throughout the
OL,19,Fregion, to treat and support children
OL,20,Fand their families who have a range of
OL,21,Fcomplex needs.
